column5: Fished Sunday on Lake Erie....got 17 walleye...one short of the limit.  Dipsy divers, bottom bouncers, and leadcore were the hot ticket.
nice work! I was just on the other side Sunday having the same luck
Dougie you're on fire this summer! Glad to see you're getting out on the water and having fun.

Fished out of crystal beach Sunday 55ft using harnesses off riggers and dipseys. Riggers 5 & 10 ft off bottom and smaller dipseys on a 3 setting 150 & 200 back. Went 13/19 on eyes and had a bonus 4 silvers and one big ol sheepie by 11am. Bigger harnesses with double Colorado blades.
Lake Erie is glass and Doug's kickin' aaaaaass.  Nice eyes.

thank's krixxer glad your having too thank's mike so far it's been awesome   thank's miller congrats to you too maybe on sat i will try rigger's  thanks drew it's been on fire 89 eye's in the last 5 trip's
